             were indicted for <rs id="t18240603-39-off206" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18240603-39-off206" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18240603-39-off206" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18240603-39-cd207" type="crimeDate">20th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240603-39-off206 t18240603-39-cd207"></join>, six yards of muslin, value 10 s.; two handkerchiefs, value 20 s., and a yard of silk, value 2 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18240603-39-victim385" type="victimName">
                     James 
                     Pincott
                  <interp inst="t18240603-39-victim385" type="surname" value="Pincott"></interp>
